my.sample object contains 100 random observations of the whole population.

mytaxi object will only contain those variables in my.sample where trip_miles is greater than 0, as it doesnt make sense to include taxi trips that have not actually moved - they will faulty affect the analysis. This also results in getting rid of trip_seconds=0.

my.taxi = subset(my.sample,trip_miles>0)
